{"tid":1409422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發完夢用單程飛嘅小朋友全部入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-04T21:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T00:31:51.000Z","uid":196615,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1efe32dd9306c23387087fa687e348d54a06ee8f","tid":1409422,"uid":196615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:14:18.000Z","msg":"繼之前開咗個po希望傳違俾派飛嘅有心人知 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">$15.5是基本盤</span></strong></span>後<br />\n<br />\n地鐵站內派單程飛嘅同我入哂嚟<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dwajCS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dwajCS</a><br />\n<br />\n然後我想再提醒各位小朋友<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">萬一你張單程飛出閘哥陣失效</span></ins><br />\n你嘅選擇有三個<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一、跳閘，但係你必須要留意閘外有冇<ins>犬隻／疑似便裝犬／地鐵職員</ins>，否則你一跳就GG<br />\n二、用自己張八達通係入閘方向拍卡入，站內兜個圈三四分鐘後拍卡出閘，扣你$3.7<br />\n三、向你身邊嘅同路人求救，叫佢地幫你買張一個站嘅單程飛入閘，然後幾分鐘後入飛出閘</span></span></strong><br />\n最唔建議嘅第四個方法，保護好自己(千祈唔好除口罩)之下去客務中心補飛，真係好唔建議，好多cam影實<br />\n<br />\n各位小朋友(或者係同路同行嘅大哥哥大姐姐)請照顧好我地嘅每一個同路人，每一個未來<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">唔好臨返到屋企附近先出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b1a7df789e93316ece4504c9854f34f773dfdcaf","tid":1409422,"uid":196615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:15:42.000Z","msg":"自己推咗先<br />\n大家的小朋友大家一齊救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f6f756f1afca65ad69888bdf83a9de28fff2b3","tid":1409422,"uid":196615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:48:06.000Z","msg":"各位準備天光出動嘅三罷巴絲，幫手推俾小朋友睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655f8bbfe8aad9e7160257eff28b28efa4637629","tid":1409422,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6z1yYmX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6z1yYmX.jpg&h=e20c9467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n罷罷罷"},{"pid":"529e056200a2c23eb944fe941136156b5be82294","tid":1409422,"uid":285924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:56:09.000Z","msg":"拎自己張八達通話係邊度入閘，不過出閘時show冇入閘記錄"},{"pid":"a695c6f65eb67c170277906743385fcd3c886670","tid":1409422,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:03:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9db58ee1d8c6a3f4384e8cd81763170c26370ed","tid":1409422,"uid":261913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"529e056200a2c23eb944fe941136156b5be82294","tid":1409422,"uid":285924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:56:09.000Z","msg":"拎自己張八達通話係邊度入閘，不過出閘時show冇入閘記錄"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:05:07.000Z","msg":"帶張成人8仔，唔好用有自己o個張"},{"pid":"54e246a981ec9f5426ffb122ddde4e8c21a2773a","tid":1409422,"uid":132896,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:05:37.000Z","msg":"聽朋友講據聞發夢打機有一次出閘入飛<br />\n直情食埋張飛關羽<br />\n然後去客服照講比人食左張飛<br />\n佢問我邊度黎（我鳩答）<br />\n佢就望望我就比左張綠色出閘卡比我<br />\n唔使補錢<br />\n<br />\n唔知好彩<br />\n真係可以咁做<br />\n定係<br />\n職員信我張飛食左先咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c13aea26462d86916172866a0926c84192a8967","tid":1409422,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:09:43.000Z","msg":"唔好塞到九點完，九點十點後好多中環人好想被罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1409491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1409491</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f2c8bf56b10ce0f8f8662a4507e64a068